  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Saying that you are mutilating the animal to protect people from mutilation poaching is absurd]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[because either way the rhino is mutilated.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[It's an attack on the animal.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[It doesn't help conservation,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[it just tries to take out the monetary component of the slaughter.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e9"><![CDATA[Bad way to go.]]></edu>
